|  00:14.2	| Audio device	| AMD/ATI Intel HDA |	1002:4383	 	| snd_hda_intel	| Carte-mère	   |
|  01:00.0	| VGA (GPU)	| GTX-260		  | 	10de:05e2		| nouveau		        | Linux (HOTE)	   |
|  02:00.0	| VGA (GPU	| R9-270x (Video)	  | 	1002:6810		| radeon		        | VFIO (GUEST) |
